Package com.hakan.core.dependency.annotations

Annotation Interface Dependency

@Retention(RUNTIME) @Target(ANNOTATION_TYPE) public @interface Dependency
Dependency annotation to download a dependency at runtime.

  • Required Element Summary

    Required Elements
    Modifier and Type
    Required Element
    Description
    String
    artifactId
    The artifact id of the dependency.
    String
    groupId
    The group id of the dependency.
    String
    savePath
    The path of the dependency that you want to download.
    String
    version
    The version of the dependency.

    Optional Element
